-- Mubadala Development Plans to Increase Holding in Carlyle by $500 Million
-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 2010-12-16T10:07:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-16/mubadala-development-plans-to-increase-holding-in-carlyle-by-500-million.html
Mubadala Development Co. will invest
$500 million in Carlyle Group in exchange for a combination of
convertible subordinated notes and additional equity in the
Carlyle general partnership, according to an e-mailed statement
from Carlyle today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maria Ermakova at 
 mermakova@bloomberg.net  